{"tid":2097491,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"GTA岀VR!?","createTime":"2020-07-07T01:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T08:34:40.000Z","uid":148034,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"121aee3df8b7a9e75f3ca94ce005296ca7745e18","tid":2097491,"uid":148034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:08:02.000Z","msg":"遊戲商 Rockstar Games 以開發開放式世界遊戲馳名，他們的《Grand Theft Auto》和《Red Dead Redemption》系列都極受玩家歡迎。最近有消息指 Rockstar 將會與澳洲 VR 遊戲開發商 Video Games Deluxe 合作，開發一款 AAA 級開放式式世界 VR 遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n一般遊戲玩家可能對 Video Games Deluxe 的名字比較陌生，他們是 VR 遊戲《LA: Noire The VR Case Files》的開發商，這家澳洲公司日前在專業社交平台 LinkedIn 宣佈和 Rockstar 合作開發新開放式世界 VR 遊戲大作的消息，又表示 2020 年是他們跟 Rockstar 合作的第七年，他們對這個突破性項目相當興奮。<br />\nVideo Games Deluxe 除了公佈新遊戲項目的消息，同時亦宣佈新的職位空缺，包括高級程式員、引擎程式員、設計師和動畫師，全部都會在他們的悉尼工作室上班。所有職位空缺都與上述的 AAA 級 VR 遊戲項目有關，但招聘廣告並未有透露其他有關遊戲的進一步資訊，所以未知是全新的題材，還是 Rockstar 現有遊戲系列的延伸。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/07/07/la-noire-the-vr-case-files-developer-is-working-on-an-open-world-vr-game-with-rockstar/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F07%2F07%2Fla-noire-the-vr-case-files-developer-is-working-on-an-open-world-vr-game-with-rockstar%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=f07f483d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/07/07/la-noire-the-vr-case-files-developer-is-working-on-an-open-world-vr-game-with-rockstar/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"1e636aa0c9a8f9ee6227bee376c334ca94679bcb","tid":2097491,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:16:56.000Z","msg":"gta VI 幾時出"},{"pid":"e90174e78e53629ece4f1d1d8269a6cbc264cd6e","tid":2097491,"uid":148034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1e636aa0c9a8f9ee6227bee376c334ca94679bcb","tid":2097491,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:16:56.000Z","msg":"gta VI 幾時出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:27:55.